<sect1 id="dir_73f976e4cfb02d3a04525286c98fa7b3_1autotoc_md271">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::health::types</title><para>Type definitions for the health system.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_73f976e4cfb02d3a04525286c98fa7b3_1autotoc_md272">
<title>Types</title><para><table rows="3" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Type  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Description  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>HealthDepletedBehavior</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Bitmask flags controlling the response when health reaches zero  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>HealthChangeContext</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Context struct describing a health modification  </para>
</entry></row>
