<sect1 id="dir_73f976e4cfb02d3a04525286c98fa7b3_1autotoc_md273">
<title>HealthDepletedBehavior</title><para>Bitmask enum with values:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>None</computeroutput> – No action</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>Despawn</computeroutput> – Queue the entity for despawning</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>DeadTag</computeroutput> – Attach a DeadTagComponent</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Supports bitwise operators and <computeroutput>hasHealthDepletedFlag()</computeroutput> for testing.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_73f976e4cfb02d3a04525286c98fa7b3_1autotoc_md274">
<title>HealthChangeContext</title><para>Lightweight struct carrying:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>interactionContext</computeroutput> – An <computeroutput>InteractionContext</computeroutput> describing target, instigator, causer, and contact point</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>delta</computeroutput> – Signed health delta (negative for damage, positive for healing)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
